data.description: You do not want to miss this Beautiful Garden Home. The house features a recently renovated kitchen, new flooring, built in bar, built in entertainment center and a built in bookcase with lighting. The incredible living space sits in an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings. It sits on a corner lot with a side entry garage. The landscaping was professionally done to create a charming curb appeal. The mature Oak Trees surround the home and offer an amazing backdrop. There are two private spacious master suites and each has upgraded vanities in their bathrooms. There is a flex room that can be utilized as an office, eat in kitchen or additional living space. There are many unique and upgraded features in this home including a Metal Roof. The Metal Roof and AC were replaced approximately 3 years ago. This small quiet neighborhood is centrally located and secluded.  The pride in ownership is evident throughout the neighborhood.
